actly;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4. 2</span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">名挂职干部代表发言各<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>分钟（第五批挂职干部先进人个人<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名，第六定点扶贫与现代农业挂职干部<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>名）。（由省委组织部通知<span lang=\"EN-US\">9:50</span>－<span lang=\"EN-US\">10:05</span>分）<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25pt;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">省委常委、农工委主任李昌平讲话（讲话基础材料由省扶贫移民局准备）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25pt;text-indent:30.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:1.94;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:黑体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\">九、会议经费<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25pt;text-indent:31.7pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:16pt;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;\">会议及会议相关经费由省扶贫移民局在部门预算专项经费中列支。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:25pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体;color:black;font-size:22pt;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:25pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactl